{"tid":1534253,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"welp","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:03:45.000Z","uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0b868733166f3874457b9b57e336fcce2eb2196c","tid":1534253,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8d60da469e778284380b05313e06c50a25d568","tid":1534253,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d31397aa8e3d1f2c0f43a24c0f9ca536f732de6d","tid":1534253,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=8672b96e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 908都要照上街<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d48f8579b9cd81385255beab9d7e4b33b75c2137","tid":1534253,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金  全民提款日</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13 00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13 00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"6fb935de6699fb45f4a85da3e691baae172d68c2","tid":1534253,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"港女加油"},{"pid":"83c5d892e184f089def2012f939d024b1e7a5898","tid":1534253,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b83489d4a6d04126d1655dcab4376ad721d48d3","tid":1534253,"uid":275090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:01:59.000Z","msg":"got it"},{"pid":"b5a405712c6b3e3a6dd44b672b165d20855db00d","tid":1534253,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"wwwwwww♪( &acute;▽｀)"},{"pid":"7c59c33dfdf22524f29cc95c3985de